data.description: Welcome to this beautiful and spacious single-family home located within the heart of Temple Terrace. This 4 bedroom, 3.5 bath home boasts 2,766 square feet of living space and an additional 1,600 square feet of screened in patio space. Step into the kitchen and discover a culinary haven. It offers an abundance of granite counter space, perfect for meal preparation and entertaining. But that's not all; wine enthusiasts will appreciate the convenience of a generously sized wine cooler, adding a touch of luxury to your everyday living. Beyond the kitchen, you'll discover the convenience of two extra refrigerators—one on the porch and another in the laundry room.  Experience the perfect ambiance in both the dining room and family room with a brand-new lighting system. Revel in the modern elegance of LED lights that not only brighten your spaces but also come with convenient dimmer controls.   The four generously sized bedrooms provide ample space for your family and guests. The master bedroom is your sanctuary within the home complete with a walk-in-closet and an en-suite bathroom including a walk-in shower and jacuzzi tub. This primary suite also features 2 large walk-in closets. Two of the home's bathrooms have recently undergone beautiful remodels and what sets this home apart is its commitment to accessibility, with all bathrooms featuring handicap fixtures for added convenience. Additionally, the step down to the Florida room has been thoughtfully equipped with removable ramps, as are the doors leading to the outdoors, ensuring ease of access for all.   Step onto the expansive 40' x 40' screened porch with hurricane-rated roof—a true outdoor haven that's perfect for both entertaining and unwinding. This inviting space features the comfort of four ceiling fans, creating a gentle breeze on warm days, while a commercial vent over the barbecue ensures smoke-free grilling. This porch is your all-season retreat. Discover serenity in your newly fenced-in backyard with a stunning, well-maintained flower garden that's bursting with vibrant blooms. The yard is equipped with an automatic sprinkler system, ensuring hassle-free lawn and garden maintenance for your convenience. Enjoy easy access to the sheds and arbor with a seamlessly integrated cement walkway in the backyard. You'll love the convenience of two oversized sheds in the backyard with one of shed’s being fully air-conditioned and equipped with built-in workbenches.  The spacious 2-car garage offers ample parking and storage space along with a freezer for extra storage. Additionally, a water softener has been thoughtfully installed in the garage and the hot water heater was replaced in 2023. This property comes with a paid-up termite protection contract with Massey in effect until June 2024. Additionally, there is an active fertilizer and pest control contract, ensuring that your home and landscape stay healthy and pest-free.  You'll enjoy peace of mind knowing that this home is equipped with a battery-powered generator that activates automatically during power outages.  This property is nestled in the highly sought-after area of Temple Terrace, offering easy access to I-75. Vibrant parks await nearby for outdoor enthusiasts or tee off at the renowned Temple Terrace Country Club.
